Class GradebookEntityProducer

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextObserver, EntityProducer, EntityTransferrer, HandlesImportable

    public class GradebookEntityProducer
extends BaseEntityProducer
implements ContextObserver, EntityTransferrer, HandlesImportable
    Implements the Sakai EntityProducer approach to integration of tool-specific storage with site management.
